{"tid":788483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得港豬呢個名起得真係好","createTime":"2018-08-21T13:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T04:39:26.000Z","uid":173357,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c4e54aa851c5f6ce3127a5bf4859d6dd37535e","tid":788483,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"今個月去咗廣東個三線城市半個月，起初覺得只係一個鄉下地方，當去度下假。點知深入咗佢地既生活之後，又覺得其實唔錯，住過千呎大屋，小朋友可以有足夠空間活動，出入小車代步，一有時間就周圍去玩，周圍去食！生活壓力少！反觀香港，生活擠迫，壓力大，雖然話係唔會餓死人，對好多打工仔黎講真係冇咩生活質素可言，連收工想有個安樂窩釋放下壓力都唔得！真係好似被人圈養咗既豬！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹個人意見，不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7ef4b73d1acb134c54015d5b763f50bd55fcac","tid":788483,"uid":146917,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔過去住？"},{"pid":"5447212fb8a4290332b29bf3c20cb99c9daf2a91","tid":788483,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"要走你大可以走 你放唔低香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aba516cf61cd687060379be70c29a09d1ab5d2","tid":788483,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9f7ef4b73d1acb134c54015d5b763f50bd55fcac","tid":788483,"uid":146917,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔過去住？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"補充下，冇人脈冇特別技能就唔好話上去發展，因為唔夠人爭"},{"pid":"25f782c754e14062c488c33f57899446aac73318","tid":788483,"uid":146917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"34aba516cf61cd687060379be70c29a09d1ab5d2","tid":788483,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9f7ef4b73d1acb134c54015d5b763f50bd55fcac","tid":788483,"uid":146917,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔過去住？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"補充下，冇人脈冇特別技能就唔好話上去發展，因為唔夠人爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:50:18.